These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, crime
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, blend
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, december
1. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime    | musical |
| Cigar         | blend | havana    |
| Birthday     | march     | december      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different pets are kept: lizard, cat
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, aconite
There 2 different types of food: lime, nectarine
1. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the person who growssunflower is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Pet      | cat  | lizard   |
| Flower   | aconite | sunflower  |
| Food     | nectarine   | lime |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: ivory, emerald
2 different pets are kept: pony, snake
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, engineer
1. the person who likes emerald is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Color         | ivory   | emerald  |
| Pet   | snake | pony  |
| Job         | bartender   | engineer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
