The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, april
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |
| Movie-Genre        | spy      | western  |
| Music-Genre       | hip-hop     | gospel    |
| Birthday   | december | april |

