City: paris, edinburgh
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, dancer
1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person eating lime##1
2. the coach is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Food         | lime    | grapes    |
| City   | edinburgh     | paris      |
| Job         | coach | dancer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, balloon-flower
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, singing
2 different games are played: billiard, canasta
1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
3. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Flower    | balloon-flower | azalea     |
| Hobby     | singing | drawing |
| Game   | canasta | billiard    |

 #################################

 
