There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, montecristo
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Sport           | rugby     | skateboarding |
| Beverage   | lemonade | almond-milk  |
| Cigar     | montecristo      | vegafina |

