2 different games are played: billiard, scrabble
The people have 2 different jobs:  electrician, bartender
1. the person playing billiard is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
