.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, dancer
2 different games are played: billiard, whist
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, tomato
1. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the chef is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Job         | dancer | chef |
| Game   | billiard     | whist     |
| Food           | tomato          | blueberry     |

