.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
2 different games are played: chess, monopoly
House: cape-cod, wooden
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk
1. the person playing chess is in an odd position##4
2. the wooden house is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Game   | chess | monopoly |
| House   | cape-cod  | wooden  |
| Beverage     | almond-milk | 7up    |

 